Package: airsetup
Title: Setup AI-Assisted R Analysis Project Structures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("gestimation", "Toolkit", , "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight workflow infrastructure for setting up controlled
    AI-assisted statistical analysis projects with R. The package creates
    folder structures, AGENTS.md guidance, specification templates, Checkpoint
    QC templates, software inventory templates, traceability logs, and project
    structure checks. It does not implement statistical analysis functions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
